# tokless
# CLI tool designed to simplify the installation and management of token-saving plugins for AI coding assistants (https://github.com/HoangP8/tokless)

# To install and configure tokless plugins (e.g., rtk, caveman, codegraph):
tokless

# To display the current configuration status and verify installed tools:
tokless doctor

# To build a project code graph index in the current directory:
tokless index

# To check for updates and upgrade installed plugins:
tokless update

# To uninstall tokless and remove all changes made to the system:
tokless uninstall
